Test "add reserves to empty contract"
    NewComptroller
    ListedBToken ZRX bZRX initialExchangeRate:1e9
    Assert Equal (BToken bZRX ExchangeRate) (Exactly 1e9)
    Erc20 ZRX Faucet Root 3e18
    From Root (Erc20 ZRX Approve bZRX 6e18)
    AddReserves 2e18 bZRX
    Assert Equal (Erc20 ZRX TokenBalance bZRX) (Exactly 2e18)
    Assert Equal (Erc20 ZRX TokenBalance Root) (Exactly 1e18)
    Assert Equal (BToken bZRX Reserves) (Exactly 2e18)
