Test "add reserves failures"
    NewComptroller
    ListedBToken ZRX bZRX initialExchangeRate:1e9
    Assert Equal (BToken bZRX ExchangeRate) (Exactly 1e9)
    Assert Equal (BToken bZRX Reserves) (Exactly 0e18)
    Erc20 ZRX Faucet Root 2e18
    AllowFailures
    AddReserves 2e18 bZRX
    Assert Revert "revert Insufficient allowance"
    Assert Equal (Erc20 ZRX TokenBalance bZRX) (Exactly 0e18)
    Assert Equal (Erc20 ZRX TokenBalance Root) (Exactly 2e18)
    Assert Equal (BToken bZRX Reserves) (Exactly 0e18)
    -- unchanged
    Assert Equal (BToken bZRX ExchangeRate) (Exactly 1e9)

